      <context id="context_N10032_N1002F_N10001">
         <p>In a <ph keyref="GR_s"/> deployment, the password for <option>process_engine</option> must be changed on
            the standby site (typically, Site B) too.</p>
      </context>
      <steps id="steps_uxn_xpq_clb">
         <step id="step_N10043_N1003F_N1002F_N10001">
            <cmd>Perform the instructions from <xref keyref="299a6f2f109ce089c15134a732aadc5d"/> to change the
               password on both VMs of the standby site.</cmd>
            <info>
               <p>
                  <note id="note_N10054_N10051_N1004E_N10043_N1003F_N1002F_N10001">
                     <p>Do not start <ph keyref="nsoProductName_s"/> service on the standby
                        site.</p>
                  </note>
               </p>
            </info>
         </step>
      </steps>
   </taskbody>
